quran[269]{c,v,t}:
  18,75,"qal alkhadir lmwsa meatbana wmdhkrana: 'alam 'aqul lak 'iinak lan tastatie maei sbrana ealaa ma taraa min afealy mimaa lam tuhit bih khubrana?"
  18,76,"qal musaa lh: 'iin sa'altuk ean shay' baed hadhih almarat fatrkny wala tsahbny, qad blght aledhr fi shany walam tqsr; hayth akhbrtany 'aniy ln 'astatie maeak sbrana"
  18,77,"fdhhb musaa walkhadir hataa 'ataya 'ahl qryt, ftlba minhum teamana ealaa sabil aldyaft, famtne 'ahl alqaryat ean dyafthma, fawajada fiha haytana mayla ywshk 'ana ysqt, feddal alkhadir maylah hataa sar mstwyana, qal lah mwsa: law shit lakhdht ealaa hadha aleamal ajrana tsrfh fi thsyl teamna hayth lm ydyfwna"
  18,78,"qal alkhadir lmwsa: hdha waqt alfiraq bayni wbynk, sakhbrk bima ankrt ely min afealy alty feltha, walati lam tastatie sbrana ealaa tarak alsuwal eanha wal'inkar ely fyha"
  18,79,"ama alsafinat alty khrqtha fa'iinaha kanat lanas masakin yaemalun fi albahr ealayha seyana wara' alrzq, fa'aradtu 'an 'aeibaha bdhlk alkhrq; li'ana 'amamahum mlkana yakhudh kula safinat salihatan ghsbana min ashabha"
  18,80,"wama alghulam aldhy qtlth fkan fi ealim allah kafrana, wakan abwh wa'umah mwminayn, fakhashina law baqi alghulam hyana lahml waldyh ealaa alkufr waltghyan; li'ajal mhbthma 'iiaah 'aw llhajt 'ilyh"
  18,81,fardna 'ana yubdil allah 'abawayh biman hu khayr minh slahana wdynana wbrana bhma
  18,82,"wama alhayit aldhy eddalt maylah hataa astwa fa'iinah kan lighulamayn yatimayn fi alqaryat alati fiha aljdar, wakan tahtah kanz lahuma min aldhahab walfdt, wakan 'abuhuma rajulaan salhana, fa'arad rabuk 'an ykbara wyblgha qwthma, wayastakhrija kanzahuma rahmatan min rabik bhma, wama felt ya musaa jmye aldhy raytany feltuh ean 'amri wamin tilqa' nfsy, wa'iinama faealtuh ean 'amr allh, dhlk aldhy bayant lak 'asbabih hu eaqibat al'umur alty lam tastatie sbrana ealaa tarak alsuwal eanha wal'inkar ely fyha"
  18,83,"wysalk -ayha alrswl- hwla' almushrikun min qawmik ean khabar dhi alqarnayn almalik alsalh, qul lhm: saqss ealaykum minh dhikrana ttdhkrwnh, wtetbrwn bh"
  18,84,"'ina mkknna lah fi alard, wataynah min kuli shay' asbabana wtrqana, yatawasal biha 'iilaa ma yurid min fath almadayin wqhr al'aeda' waghayr dhlk"
  18,85,fakhdh bitilk al'asbab waltrq bijidin wajthad
  18,86,"hta 'iidha wasal dhu alqarnayn 'iilaa maghrib alshams wajadaha fi mar'aa aleayn ka'anaha taghrub fi eayn hart dhat tin aswd, wawajad eind mghrbha qwmana. qlna: ya dha alqarnayn 'iimaa 'an tueadhibhum balqtl 'aw ghyrh, 'iin lam yqru btwhyd allh, wa'iimaa 'an tahasun 'ilyhm, ftelmhm alhudaa wtbsrhm alrshad"
  18,87,"qal dhu alqrnyn: amma man zalam nafsah minhum fkfr brbh, fasawf nueadhibuh fi aldnya, thuma yarjie 'iilaa rbh, fayueadhibuh edhabana ezymana fi nar jhnm"
  18,88,"wama man aman minhum birabih fsddaq bih wwhhadh waeamil btaeth falah aljanat thwabana min allh, wsnhsn 'ilyh, wnlyn lah fi alqawl wnyssir lah almeamlt"
  18,89,thm raje dhu alqarnayn 'iilaa almashriq mtbeana al'asbab alty aetah allah 'iyaha
  18,90,"hta 'iidha wasal 'iilaa matlie alshams wajadaha tatlue ealaa qawm lays lahum bina' ystrhm, wala shajar yzlhm min alshms"
  18,91,"kdhlk waqad 'ahat eilmuna bima eindah min alkhayr walasbab alezymt, haythuma twjjah wsar"
  18,92,thm sar dhu alqarnayn akhdhana bialturuq walasbab alty mnhnaha 'iyah
  18,93,"hta 'iidha wasal 'iilaa ma bayn aljblyn alhajzyn lamaa wra'hma, wajad min dunihima qwmana, laa yakadun yaerifun kalam ghyrhm"
  18,94,"qalu ya dha alqrnyn: 'inn yajuj wamajuj -whma ammatan ezymtan min bani adm- mufsidun fi al'ard b'ihlak alharth walnsl, fahal najeal lak ajrana, wnjme lak malana ealaa 'an tajeal baynana wabaynahum hajzana yahul baynana wbynhm?"
  18,95,"qal dhu alqrnyn: ma aetanyh rabiy min almalik waltmkyn khayr li min malkm, fa'aeinuni biquat minkum 'ajeal baynakum wabaynahum sdana"
  18,96,"aetwny qate alhdyd, hataa 'iidha jawu bih wwdewh whadhu bih janibi aljblyn, qal llemal: ajjiju alnar, hataa 'iidha sar alhadid klh narana, qal: aetwny nhasana 'ufrghh elyh"
  18,97,"fma aistataeat yajuj wamajuj 'ana tusaeid fawq alsd; lartfaeh wmlasth, wama astataeuu 'ana ynqbwh min asflh lbed eardih wqwth"
  18,98,"qal dhu alqrnyn: hdha aldhy bnyth hajzana ean fasad yajuj wamajuj rahmat min rabiy balnas, fa'iidha ja' waed rabiy bkhrwj yajuj wamajuj jaealah dakaa' mnhdmana mstwyana balard, wakan waed rabiy hqqana"
  18,99,"wtrkna yajuj wamajuj -ywm yatiahum waeduna- yamuj bedhm fi bed mkhtltyn; lkthrthm, wanufikh fi \"alqrn\" llbeth, fjmena alkhalq jmyeana llhsab waljza'"
  18,100,"werdna jahanam llkafryn, wabrznaha lahum lnryhm su' eaqbthm"
  18,101,"aldhyn kanat 'aeyunuhum fi aldunya fi ghita' ean dhikri fala tbsr ayaty, wakanuu la ytyqwn smae hjjy almwslt 'iilaa al'iiman bi wbrswly"
  18,102,afzn aladhin kafaruu bi 'an yatakhidhuu eibadi alihatan min ghyry; liyakunuu 'awlia' lhm? 'iinaa 'aetadna nar jahanam lilkafirin mnzla
  18,103,"ql -ayha alrswl- lilnaas mhdhrana: hal nukhbrkm bakhsr alnaas aemala?"
  18,104,"'inhm aladhin dll eamalahum fi alhayat aldunya -whm mshrkw qawmak wghyrhm mmn dll sawa' alsbyl, falam yakun ealaa hudana wala swab- wahum yazunuwn 'anahum muhsinun fi aemalhm"
  18,105,"awlyk al'akhsarun 'aemalana hum aladhin jahaduu biayat rabihim wkdhdhabu bha, wankru liqa'ih yawm alqyamt, fbtlt aemalhm; bsbb kfrhm, fala nuqim lahum yawm alqiamat qdrana"
  18,106,dhlk almdhkwr min hbwt 'aemalahum jazawuhum nar jhnm; bsbb kufruhum biallah watkhadhhm ayatih whjj rusulah asthza'an wskhryt
  18,107,"'in aladhin amanuu by, wsddaqu rsly, waeamiluu alsalhat, lahum 'aelaa aljanat wafdlha mnzla"
  18,108,"khaldyn fiha abdana, la yuridun eanha thwwula; lrghbthm fiha whbhm lha"
  18,109,"qul -ayha alrswl-: law kan ma'an albahr hbrana llaqlam alty yaktub biha kalam allh, lnfid ma'an albahr qabl 'an tanfad kalimat allh, walaw jina bimithl albahr bharana 'ukhraa mddana lh. wafi alayat 'iithbat sifat alkalam lilah -teala- hqyqt kama ylyq bjlalh wkmalh"
  18,110,"ql -ayha alrswl- lhwla' almshrkyn: 'iinama 'ana bashar mithlukum ywha 'ily min rabiy 'anama 'ilhkm 'ilh wahd, fman kan yakhaf eadhab rabih wayarju thwabh yawm lqayh, falyaemal eamalana salhana lirabih mwafqana lshreh, wala yushrik fi alebadt maeah ahdana ghyrh"
  19,1,(khyes) sabaq alkalam ealaa alhrwf almqttaet fi 'awal surat albqrt
  19,2,"hdha dhikr rahmat rabik eabdah zkrya, snqsh elyk, fa'iina fi dhalik eibratan llmetbryn"
  19,3,"'idh daea rabah srana; liakun 'akmal watm 'ikhlasana llh, warja ll'ijabt"
  19,4,"qal: rabi 'iiniy kabirtu, wadief ezmy, wantshr alshyb fi rasy, walam 'akun min qibal mhrwmana min 'ijabt aldea'"
  19,5,"w'iny khafat aqarby wesbty min baed mwty 'an la yqwmu bdynk haqa alqyam, wala ydeu eibadik 'ilyk, wakanat zawjati eaqrana la tld, farzqny min eindik wldana warthana wmeynana"
  19,6,"yrth nbwwaty wnbwt al yeqwb, wajeal hdha alwld mrdyana mink wamin ebadk"
  19,7,"ya zakariaa 'inna nubashiruk b'ijabt deayk, qad wahabna lak ghlamana aismuh yhya, lm nusamm ahdana qablih bhdha alasm"
  19,8,"qal zakariaa mtejbana: rbb kayf yakun li ghlam, wakanat amra'ati eaqrana la tld, wa'ana qad balaght alnihayat fi alkibar waraqat alezm?"
  19,9,"qal almalak mjybana zakariaa emma tejjab mnh: hkdha al'amr kama taqul min kawn amra'atak eaqrana, wblwghk min alkibar etyana, wlknn rabik qal: khalq yahyaa ealaa hadhih alkyfyt 'amr sahl hyin elya, thuma dhikr allah subhanah lzkrya ma hu 'aejab mimaa sa'al eanh fqal: waqad khalaqtuk 'ant min qibal yhya, walam tk shyyana mdhkwrana wala mwjwdana"
  19,10,"qal zakariaa ziadat fi atmynanh: rbb ajeal liy elamt ealaa thqquq ma bashsharatny bih almlaykt, qal: elamtk 'an la tuqadar ealaa kalam alnaas mdt thalath layal wayamha, wa'ant sahih meafa"
  19,11,"fkhrj zakariaa ealaa qawmih min mslah, wahu almakan aldhy bushshir fih balwld, fashar 'ilyhm: 'an sabbihu allah sbahana wmsa'an shkrana lah teala"
  19,12,"flma wld yhya, wabalagh mblghana yafham fih alkhitabi, 'amrih alllah 'an yakhudh altawrat bjdd wajthad bqwlh: ya yahyaa khudh altawrat bijidin wajthad bhfz alfazha, wafahm meanyha, waleamal bha, waetynah alhikmat wahusn alfhm, wahu saghir alsn"
  19,13,"watynah rahmatan wmhbt min eindina wthart min aldhnwb, wakan khayfana mtyeana lilah teala, mwdyana fraydh, mjtnbana mharmh"
  19,14,"wkan barrana biwalidayh mtyeana lhma, walam yakun mtkbrana ean taeat rbh, wala ean taeat waldyh, wala easyana lrbh, wala lwaldyh"
  19,15,"wslam min allah ealaa yahyaa wa'aman lah yawm wulid, wayawm ymwt, wayawm yubeth min qabrih hyana"
  19,16,"wadhkr - 'ayuha alrasul - fi hadha alquran khabar maryam 'iidh tbaedt ean ahlha, fatakhadhat laha mkanana mimaa yali alshrq enhm"
  19,17,"fjelt min dun 'ahliha strana ystrha eanhum waean alnas, fa'arsalna 'iilayha almlak jbryl, ftmththal laha fi surat 'iinsan tamin alkhalq"
  19,18,"qalt maryam lh: 'iiniy astjyr balrhmn mink 'ana tnalny bisu' 'iin kunt mmn yataqi allh"
  19,19,"qal laha almalak: 'iinama 'ana rasul rabik bethny 'ilyk; li'ahab lak ghlamana tahrana min aldhnwb"
  19,20,"qalt maryam llmalak: kayf yakun li ghlam, walam yamsasni bashar bnkah hlal, walam ak zany?"
  19,21,"qal laha almalak: hkdha al'amr kama tsfyn min 'anah lm yamsask bshr, walam tkwny baghiana, wlkn rabik qal: al'amr ely shl; waliakun hdha alghulam elamt lilnaas tadulu ealaa qudrat allah teala, warahmatan mnna bih wbwaldth wbalnas, wakan wujud eisaa ealaa hadhih alhalat qada' sabqana mqddarana, mstwrana fi allwh almhfwz, fla bd min nfwdhh"
  19,22,"fhmlt maryam balghlam baed 'an nufikh jbryl fi jayb qmysha, fwslt alnfkht 'iilaa rahimiha, fawaqae alhml bsbb dhlk, ftbaedt bih 'iilaa makan baeid ean alnas"
  19,23,"faljaha talq alhml 'iilaa jidhe alnakhlat fqalt: ya laytani mtt qabl hdha alyawm, wakunt shyyana laa yueraf, wala yudhkar, wala yudraa man ana?"
  19,24,"fnadaha jbryl 'aw eysa: 'an la tahzny, qad jaeal rabuk tahtak jadwl ma'"
  19,25,wharriky jidhe alnakhlat tusaqit ealayk rtbana ghaddana juni min saeth
  19,26,"fkly min alrtb, washrabi min alma' wtyby nfsana balmwlwd, fa'iina ra'ayt min alnaas ahdana fsalk ean amrk faquli lh: 'iiniy 'awjabt ealaa nafsi lilah skwtana, falan 'ukalim alyawm ahdana min alnaas. walskwt kan tebdana fi shrehm, dun shryet muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm"
  19,27,"fatt maryam qawmaha tahmil mwlwdha min almakan albeyd, falamaa ra'awha kdhlk qaluu lha: ya maryam laqad jit amrana ezymana mftra"
  19,28,"ya 'ukht alrajul alsaalih harun ma kan 'abuk rajul su' yati alfwahsh, wama kanat 'umuk aimra'at su' tati albigha'"
  19,29,"fashart maryam 'iilaa mwlwdha eisaa lysalwh wyklmwh, faqaluu mnkryn elyha: kayf nukalim man la yazal fi mhdh tiflaan rdyeana?"
  19,30,"qal eisaa wahu fi mhdh yrde: 'iiniy eabd allh, qadaa b'ietayy alktab, wahu al'injyl, wajaealani nbyana"
  19,31,"wjelny eazim alkhayr walnfe haythuma wujidtu, wa'awsani bialmuhafazat ealaa alsalat wa'iita' alzakat ma baqiat hyana"
  19,32,"wjelny barrana bwaldty, walam yajealni mtkbrana wala shqyana, easyana lrby"
  19,33,"walslamt wal'aman ely min allah yawm wulidtu, wayawm amwt, wayawm 'ubeth hyana yawm alqyamt"
  19,34,"dhlk aldhy qasasna ealayk - 'ayuha alrasul - sftah wkhbrah hu eisaa abn mrym, min ghyr shakin wala mryt, bal hu qwl alhaqi aladhi shaka fih alyhwd walnsara"
  19,35,"ma kan lilah taealaa wala ylyq bih 'an yatakhidh min eibadih wkhalqh wldana, tnzzah wtqddas ean dhlk, 'iidha qadaa amrana min al'umur waradh, sghyrana 'aw kbyrana, lm ymtne elyh, wa'iinama yaqul lh: \"kn\", fayakun kama sha'h waradh"
  19,36,"wqal eisaa lqwmh: wa'iina allah aladhi 'adeukum 'iilayh hu wahdah rabiy warabukum faebuduh wahdah la sharik lh, fa'ana wa'antum swa' fi aleubudiat walkhdwe lh, hadha hu altariq aldhy la aewjaj fyh"
  19,37,"fakhtlft alfiraq min 'ahl alkitab fima baynahum fi 'amr eisaa ealayh alslam, faminhum ghal fih wahum alnsara, faminhum man qal: hu allh, waminhum man qal: hu abn allh, waminhum man qal: thalith thalathat - taealaa allah eamaa yaqulun -, waminhum jaf eanh wahum alyhwd, qalu: sahr, wqalu: abn yusif alnjar, fhlak liladhin kafaruu min shuhud yawm eazim alhwl, wahu yawm alqyamt"
  19,38,"ma ashdd smeahm wbsrhm yawm alqyamt, yawm yaqdumwn ealaa allh, hin la yanfaeuhum dhlk!! lkn alzaalimun alyawm fi hadhih aldunya fi dhhab byin ean alhq"
  19,39,"wandhr - 'ayuha alrasul - alnaas yawm alnadamat hin yuqda alamr, wyuja' balmwt kannah kbsh amlh, fyudhbah, wyufsl bayn alkhlq, fysyr 'ahl al'iiman 'iilaa aljnt, wa'ahl alkufr 'iilaa alnar, wahum alyawm fi hadhih aldunya fi ghaflat emma 'undhru bh, fahum la ysdqwn, wala yaemalun aleamal alsalh"
  19,40,"'ina nahn alwarithun llard wman ealayha bfnayhm wbqayna baedihim whukmna fyhm, wa'iilayna masirihim whsabhm, fnjazyhm ealaa aemalhm"
  19,41,"wadhkur - 'ayuha alrasul - lqwmk fi hadha alquran qisat 'iibrahim - ealayh alslam - 'iinah kan eazim alsdq, wmin arfe 'anbia' allah taealaa mnzlt"
  19,42,"'idh qal li'abih azr: ya 'abat li'ayi shay' taebud min al'asnam ma la yasmae wala ybsr, wala yadfae eank shyyana min dun allh?"
  19,43,"ya abt, 'iina allah 'aetani min aleilm ma lam yetk, fa'aqbal mny, watbeny 'iilaa ma adewk 'ilyh, arshdk 'iilaa altariq alsawii aldhy la tdll fyh"
  19,44,"ya abt, la tutie alshaytan ftebd hadhih alasnam; 'iina alshaytan kan llrhmn mkhalfana mstkbrana ean taeat allh"
  19,45,"ya abt, 'iiniy 'akhaf 'an tamut ealaa kfrk, fymassak eadhab min alrhmn, fatakun lilshaytan qrynana fi alnar"
  19,46,"qal 'abu 'iibrahim labnh: amerd 'ant ean eibadat alihati ya 'ibrahym? layin lam tantah ean sabbiha laqtlnnak rmyana balhjart, wadhhb eaniy fala tlqny, wala tklmny zmanana tawilaan min aldhr"
  19,47,"qal 'iibrahim labyh: salam ealayk miniy fala ynalk miniy ma tkrh, wasawf 'adeu allah lak balhdayt walmghfr. 'iina rabiy kan rhymana rwwfana bhaly yjybny 'iidha dewth"
  19,48,"wafarqkm walhtkm alty tebdwnha min dun allh, wa'adeu rabiy mkhlsana, easaa 'an la ashqa biduea' rby, fala yetyny ma asalh"
  19,49,"flma farqhm walhthm alty yebdwnha min dun allah razaqnah min alwld: 'ishaq, wayaequb bin 'ishaq, wjelnahma nbyayn"
  19,50,"wwhbna lahum jamieaan min rahmatina fadlana la yhsa, wajaealna lahum dhkrana hsnana, wthna'an jamilana baqyana fi alnas"
  19,51,"wadhkr - 'ayuha alrasul - fi alquran qisat musaa - ealayh alslam - 'iinah kan mustafaa mkhtarana, wakan rasulana nbyana min 'uwli aleazm min alrsl"
  19,52,"wnadyna musaa min nahiat jabal tawar \"syna'\" alyumnaa min mwsa, wqrrabnah fshrrafnah bmnajatna lh. wafi hdha 'iithbat sifat alkalam lilah - taealaa - kama ylyq bjlalh wkmalh"
  19,53,wwhbna lmwsa min rahmatina 'akhah harun nbyana ywydh wywazrh
  19,54,"wadhkur - 'ayuha alrasul - fi hadha alquran khabar 'iismaeil ealayh alslam, 'iinah kan sadqana fi waedah falam yaeid shyyana 'iilaa wffa bh, wakan rasulana nbyana"
  19,55,"wkan yamur 'ahlah b'iqam alsalat wa'iita' alzkat, wakan eind rabih eaza wajala mrdyana enh"
  19,56,"wadhkr - 'ayuha alrasul - fi hadha alquran khabar 'iidris ealayh alslam, 'iinah kan eazim alsidq fi qawlah wemlh, nbyana ywha 'ilyh"
  19,57,"wrfaena dhikrh fi alealmyn, wmnzlth bayn almqrbyn, fakan eali aldhkr, eali almnzlt"
  19,58,"hwla' aladhin qsst ealayk khbrhm 'ayuha alrswl, hum aladhin 'aneam allah ealayhim bfdlh wtwfyqh, fajaealahum 'anbia' min dhuriyat adm, wmin dhuriyat man hamalna mae nuh fi alsfynt, wamin dhuriyat 'ibrahym, wamin dhuriyat yeqwb, wmmman hadayna lil'iiman wastfyna llrsalt walnbuwwat, 'iidha ttla ealayhim ayat alrhmn almutadamanat ltwhydh whjjh khrru sajidin lilah khdweana, wastkant, wbkawa min khashyatih subhanah wteala"
  19,59,"fata min baed hwla' almneam ealayhim 'atbae saw' tarakuu alsalat klha, 'aw fwtu wqtha, 'aw tarakuu arkanha wwajbatha, watabaeuu ma ywafq shhwathm wylaymha, fasawf yalqawn shrana wdlala wakhaybat fi jhnm"
  19,60,"lkn man tab minhum min dhanbih waman birabih waeamil salhana tsdyqana ltwbth, fawlyk yaqbal allah twbthm, wydkhlwn aljanat mae almuminin wala yunqaswn shyyana min 'aemalahum alsalht"
  19,61,"jnat khld wa'iiqamat daymt, wahi alati wueid alrhmn biha eibadah bialghayb famanu biha walam yrwha, 'iina waed allah lieibadih bhdhh aljanat at la mhalt"
  19,62,"la yasmae 'ahl aljanat fiha klamana batilana lkn yasmaeun salamana tahiatan lhm, walahum rizquhum fiha min altaeam walshrab daymana, kulama shawu bukratan weshyana"
  19,63,"tlk aljanat almwswft bitilk alsfat, hi alty nwrthha wnetyha eibadina almutaqin lna, bamtthal awamrna wajtnab nwahyna"
  19,64,"waqul - ya jbryl - lmhmd: wama natanazal - nahn almalayikat - min alsama' 'iilaa al'ard 'iilaa bi'amr rabik lna, lah ma bayn 'aydina mimaa yastaqbil min 'amr alakhrt, wama khalfana mimaa madaa min aldnya, wama bayn aldunya walakhrt, falah al'amr kuluh fi alzman walmkan, wama kan rabuk nasyana lishay' min alashya'"
  19,65,"fhw allah rabu alsmwat wal'ard wama bynhma, wmalk dhlk klh wkhalqh wmdbrh, faebudh wahdah - 'ayuha alnabiu - wasbir ealaa taeth 'ant wman tbek, lays kamithlih shay' fi dhatih wasmayh wsfath wafealh"
  19,66,"wyqwl al'iinsan alkafir mnkrana llbeth baed almwt: 'a'iidha ma mitt wfanit lasawf 'ukhraj min qbry hyana?"
  19,67,"kyf nasi hdha al'iinsan alkafir nfsh? 'awala yadhkur 'anaa khalaqnah 'awal mrt, walam yk shyyana mwjwdana?"
  19,68,"fwrbk - 'ayuha alrasul - lnjmen hwla' almnkryn llbeth yawm alqiamat mae alshyatyn, thuma lnatyn bihim 'ajmaein hawl jahanam barkyn ealaa rukabhm; lshdt maa hum fih min alhwl, laa yaqdirun ealaa alqyam"
